-- V0.1 

changed the unit of attack, decay, and release time in wtsconfig_t
  from ticks to second

modified the volume balance of default tone params
  increased volume of tirangle tones.

modifiled mid2wav.c to exit properly.
  deleted all undeleted pointers.	 

added ctplay.c and related makefiles

ctplay is an implemetation of a command line midi file player using mid2wav.
It requires SDL to compile.



